            <ab>Y72.8 (mss. 40, 400, 410, 2007, 2010, 2030, 4000, 4010, 4025, 4040, 4050, 5020):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>yasnəmca vaɱəmca aōjasca zauuarəca āfrīnāmi tauua ātarš puϑra ahurahe mazdā̊</em> dast pad ādur gāh abāz nihišn ud barsom ō urwēs nihišn</ab>   
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "At <em>yasnəmca vaɱəmca aōjasca zauuarəca āfrīnāmi tauua ātarš puϑra ahurahe mazdā̊</em>, (the <em>rāspīg</em>) has to put again his hand on the <em>ādurgāh</em> 
                and to put the <em>barsom</em> on the <em>urwēs</em>."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
    </Ritual>
